#: subscription/templates/subscription/subscriptionpage.html:349
msgid ""
"\n"
"          For the FIDE you are a Belgian.\n"
"          This means you can win the Balgian title and you can participate\n"
"          to the European and World Championships as part of the Belgian "
"team.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Voor de FIDE ben je een Belg.\n"
"Dit betekent dat je  Belgisch kampioen kan worden en dat je je aan het EK / "
"WK\n"
"kan deelnemen in het Belgische team. "

#: subscription/templates/subscription/subscriptionpage.html:356
msgid ""
"\n"
"          For the FIDE you are not a Belgian.\n"
"          This means you cannot win the Belgian title and you cannot "
"participate\n"
"          to the European and World Championships as part of the Belgian "
"team.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Voor de FIDE ben je geen Belg.\n"
"Dit betekent dat je geen Belgisch kampioen kan worden en dat je niet aan het "
"EK / WK\n"
"kan deelnemen in het Belgische team. "

#: subscription/templates/subscription/subscriptionpage.html:363
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "\n"
#| "          You are not affiliated to the FIDE.  Unless you\n"
#| "          <a href='mailto:info@bycco.be'>contact us</a> before the 15th "
#| "of March\n"
#| "          and instruct us to explicitely do otherwise,\n"
#| "          we will affiliate you as a Belgian to the FIDE,\n"
